        @BeanProperty(value="state")
public ProcessingInfo.State getState()
        It contains a state field which has transition flow: “pending” -> “in_progress” -> [“failed” | “succeeded”]. You can not use the media_id to create Tweet or other entities before the state field is set to “succeeded”.
